# GRAPHICS::SET_BINK_MOVIE_TIME

## Summary
Sets the time of the current movie

## Parameters
* **BINK_MOVIE_ID** movieId
* **FLOAT** movieTime

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
In percentage: 0.0 - 100.0
